        </div>
        <div class="modal-job">
          <div class="modal-job-header">
            <span class="modal-job-title">Shuhariko</span>
            <span class="modal-job-date">Feb 2023 - May 2025</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="modal-job-list">
            <li class="modal-job-list-item">Developed landing pages and custom CMS solutions using React</li>
            <li class="modal-job-list-item">Deployed and managed applications using AWS hosting services</li>
            <li class="modal-job-list-item">Built reusable, strongly-typed components</li>
            <li class="modal-job-list-item">Focused on frontend performance optimization and UX</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-job">
          <div class="modal-job-header">
            <span class="modal-job-title">BIOS Informática</span>
            <span class="modal-job-date">Sep 2025 - Present</span>
